  "3317890": {
    "name": "继续追寻",
    "steam_appid": 3317890,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >继续追寻是一款受大陆科幻与道教修仙启发的氛围视觉小说。游戏设定在敦煌、重庆和临海的幻魅景观中，邀请玩家探索平行维度、洞天以及超验的城市空间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/9635c37ebec735d99210c802fb460cb0.poster.avif?t=1732039899\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/9635c37ebec735d99210c802fb460cb0.webm?t=1732039899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/9635c37ebec735d99210c802fb460cb0.mp4?t=1732039899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色与剧情</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角钱江敏是一位大病初愈的年轻学者，正在寻找他的兄长。他的旅程逐渐揭示隐藏的洞天，以及关于他双瞳的谜团，推动他走向自我发现与超越。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演拥有 HMD（头戴式显示器）和无人机的钱江敏，一位寻找兄长的年轻研究员。在学者和道士的指引下，你将探索隐藏在临海古城下的神秘境界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/ac64ec038464a59ee04d906443cb5f42.poster.avif?t=1732039899\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/ac64ec038464a59ee04d906443cb5f42.webm?t=1732039899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/ac64ec038464a59ee04d906443cb5f42.mp4?t=1732039899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏操作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用 <i><strong>WASD</strong></i> 和 <i><strong>方向键</strong></i> 进行导航，按 <i><strong>Shift</strong></i> 加速，按 <i><strong>Enter</strong></i> 进入鸟瞰视角。使用 <strong><i>空格键</i></strong> 切换关卡，按住 <i><strong>i</strong></i> 键可检视特定 NPC 和位置。按 <i><strong>R</strong></i> 键重新开始关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅程中，靠近并与 <i><strong>十二面体物件</strong></i> 和其他隐藏物件互动，通过鼠标悬停或点击，深入探索游戏叙事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/590d5dad0c231b587ef8d33720378c8b.poster.avif?t=1732039899\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/590d5dad0c231b587ef8d33720378c8b.webm?t=1732039899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/590d5dad0c231b587ef8d33720378c8b.mp4?t=1732039899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >非线性探索</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏设计为非线性且没有强制性目标，着重探索和发现。你可以随时切换到任意的 14 个关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鼓励玩家漫游、发掘隐藏的空间，并拼凑出一个不完整、有缺陷但&quot;风景如画&quot;的城市肌理。这里没有固定目标——只有好奇与冒险的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/21fc6ec154a5e952e32521598c9eee5e.poster.avif?t=1732039899\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/21fc6ec154a5e952e32521598c9eee5e.webm?t=1732039899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/21fc6ec154a5e952e32521598c9eee5e.mp4?t=1732039899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >风沙敦煌</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >继续追寻将玩家带入敦煌平凡却又超验的街道，这是中国西北部一座拥有古老丝绸之路文化遗产的重要城市。你将体验日常生活的节奏，同时发掘更深层的精神与历史层面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/cd1674c1f9d29b19d97e903dffc95859.poster.avif?t=1732039899\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/cd1674c1f9d29b19d97e903dffc95859.webm?t=1732039899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/cd1674c1f9d29b19d97e903dffc95859.mp4?t=1732039899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >雾都重庆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的另一个场景设置在重庆，捕捉了毗邻四川美术学院的区域中持续的雾雨和后工业感。这种环境营造出令人着迷的超现实氛围，将艺术与城市脉络融为一体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/6c2404d1155958cd8b41bee5745254eb.poster.avif?t=1732039899\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/6c2404d1155958cd8b41bee5745254eb.webm?t=1732039899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/6c2404d1155958cd8b41bee5745254eb.mp4?t=1732039899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无碰撞感的临海</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >继续追寻主要在浙江台州临海古城展开。此场景促成一个将中国道教哲学与现代科技相连结的城市科技玄幻，为玩家提供一个反思中国传统文化中幻魅般的奇异视角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/7089aa766b901eb6fedf4a723c716e64.poster.avif?t=1732039899\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/7089aa766b901eb6fedf4a723c716e64.webm?t=1732039899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/7089aa766b901eb6fedf4a723c716e64.mp4?t=1732039899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自我民族志</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >继续追寻的每个关卡都结合了艺术、神话和冥想，创造出一个沉浸式体验。这鼓励玩家以独特的方式思考性命双修、文化遗产和现代性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/0252ad4121dbd2c8512125e94a1b04e1.poster.avif?t=1732039899\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/0252ad4121dbd2c8512125e94a1b04e1.webm?t=1732039899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317890/extras/0252ad4121dbd2c8512125e94a1b04e1.mp4?t=1732039899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与《超体》共享宇宙</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >继续追寻与《超体》VR 游戏设定在同一宇宙中，共享 NPC 和特定环境。《超体》的爱好者可以在&quot;花园传送门&quot;关卡中探索两款游戏之间的连结，获得更多的沉浸式体验。</p>",
